NOTICE — third-party runtime dependency

This project (the code in THIS repository) is licensed under MIT. It depends at
runtime on the writing engine "@actalk/inkos-core", which is a SEPARATE project
licensed under AGPL-3.0-only (https://github.com/Narcooo/inkos). That engine is
NOT included in this repository; it is fetched by `npm install`.

If you deploy this project as a network service, your use of @actalk/inkos-core
is governed by AGPL-3.0. The MIT license here applies only to the code in this
repository, not to that dependency.
